management, and utility-grade solar and wind inverters. This shift from traditional silicon to SiC creates opportunities for investors with an equity interest</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180439134/image_2180439134.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743178-wolfspeed-stock-11-billion-design-wins-not-enough", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 10:11:32"}, {"id": "4743184", "title": "November Pushes Large Global M&A Activity To 3-Quarter High", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912015932/image_912015932.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesspeople making handshakes across line, on painted asphalt\" data-id=\"912015932\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912015932/image_912015932.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912015932/image_912015932.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912015932/image_912015932.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912015932/image_912015932.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912015932/image_912015932.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912015932/image_912015932.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912015932/image_912015932.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912015932/image_912015932.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Headed into the final month, the fourth quarter is already the second-most active period in 2024 for $10 billion-plus M&amp;A announcements.</p> <p>Three M&amp;A deals with transaction values of more than $10 billion were announced during November, matching the total from</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912015932/image_912015932.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743184-november-pushes-large-global-ma-activity-3-quarter-high", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 09:50:00"}, {"id": "4743175", "title": "Customers Bancorp: The Series E Preferred Is Now The Best Income Option", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1433025794/image_1433025794.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money management with dollar appreciation.global crisis.business growth.\" data-id=\"1433025794\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1039px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1433025794/image_1433025794.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1433025794/image_1433025794.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1433025794/image_1433025794.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1433025794/image_1433025794.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1433025794/image_1433025794.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1433025794/image_1433025794.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1433025794/image_1433025794.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1433025794/image_1433025794.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">HAKINMHAN</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>Customers Bancorp (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CUBI\" title=\"Customers Bancorp, Inc.\">CUBI</a></span>) is a small regional bank based out of Pennsylvania. In addition to its common shares, the bank also offers two floating preferred shares (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CUBI.PR.E\" title=\"Customers Bancorp, Inc. PERP PFD NON CUM SER E FXD TO FLTG\">CUBI.PR.E</a></span>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CUBI.PR.F\" title=\"Customers Bancorp, Inc. PERP PFD NON CUM FIXED/FLTG SER F\">CUBI.PR.F</a>) and a baby bond (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1433025794/image_1433025794.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743175-customers-bancorp-series-e-preferred-are-now-the-best-income-option", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 09:39:27"}, {"id": "4743174", "title": "Trump, Tariffs, And Turnarounds: Why Cleveland-Cliffs Is A Top Pick For 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Old Iron Plate Embossed With \"MADE IN USA\"' data-id=\"184967527\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1020px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">joecicak</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p><em>\"This time is different\"</em> is a sarcastic phrase often used by traders to make fun of a company or asset that has appreciated a lot in value. It's based on the assumption that eventually, all bubbles pop.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743174-trump-tariffs-turnarounds-cleveland-cliffs-top-pick-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 09:35:03"}, {"id": "4743172", "title": "GBAB: High Yield Income And Diversification With Interesting Bond Mix", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1934166657/image_1934166657.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bond word in wooden blocks with coins on floor. Investment bond, Bond increasing, Raising funds and financial and banking concept.\" data-id=\"1934166657\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1934166657/image_1934166657.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1934166657/image_1934166657.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1934166657/image_1934166657.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1934166657/image_1934166657.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1934166657/image_1934166657.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1934166657/image_1934166657.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1934166657/image_1934166657.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1934166657/image_1934166657.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Wipada Wipawin</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>Many bond funds, like the Guggenheim Taxable Municipal Bond &amp; Investment Grade Debt Trust (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GBAB\" title=\"Guggenheim Taxable Municipal Bond &amp; Investment Grade Debt Trust\">GBAB</a></span>), have given up pretty much all of the price gains this year because of <a href=\"https://www.crfb.org/blogs/fed-cuts-rates-treasury-yields-are-rising#:~:text=But%20surprisingly%2C%20longer%2Dterm%20yields,a%20more%20bullish%20economic%20outlook.\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"https://www.crfb.org/blogs/fed-cuts-rates-treasury-yields-are-rising#:~:text=But%20surprisingly%2C%20longer%2Dterm%20yields,a%20more%20bullish%20economic%20outlook.\" target=\"_blank\">climbing yields</a> after the rate cuts. The</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1934166657/image_1934166657.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743172-gbab-high-yield-income-diversification-with-interesting-bond-mix", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 09:23:01"}, {"id": "4743176", "title": "Argentina ETF On Top In 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1807483415/image_1807483415.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"ETF abbreviation for Exchange Traded Fund written on wooden cube blocks with blurred stack of coins and white increasing graph line. Copy space included\" data-id=\"1807483415\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1807483415/image_1807483415.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1807483415/image_1807483415.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1807483415/image_1807483415.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1807483415/image_1807483415.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1807483415/image_1807483415.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1807483415/image_1807483415.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1807483415/image_1807483415.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1807483415/image_1807483415.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Ratana21</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Below is a look at year-to-date total returns for 46 country ETFs available to investors on US exchanges. While the US (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust\">SPY</a>) is sitting on a huge gain of 28.6% this year, the average year-to-date change for these country</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1807483415/image_1807483415.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743176-argentina-etf-on-top-in-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 09:00:00"}, {"id": "4743163", "title": "BHK: 4 Reasons Why I Am Cautious", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"forex charts\" data-id=\"165999267\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5184px\" height=\"3456px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Adam Smigielski</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The BlackRock Core Bond Trust (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BHK\" title=\"BlackRock Core Bond Trust\">BHK</a></span>) is an investment trust (\"The Trust\") which seeks to provide both current income and capital appreciation. The Trust was launched in November 2001 and currently has net assets of $582 million.</p> <p>BHK employs a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/165999267/image_165999267.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743163-bhk-cef-4-reasons-why-i-am-cautious", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 08:43:21"}, {"id": "4743159", "title": "JEPI: The Stars Are Aligning For 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1136849868/image_1136849868.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman With Spyglass Looking Out Toward Mountain Range\" data-id=\"1136849868\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1043px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1136849868/image_1136849868.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1136849868/image_1136849868.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1136849868/image_1136849868.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1136849868/image_1136849868.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1136849868/image_1136849868.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1136849868/image_1136849868.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_image